{"tid":342547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵預左蝕錢？　高鐵運作耗鉅資　港鐵主席：可由政府包底","createTime":"2017-07-31T16:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T04:54:13.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d29325ea133ea9af597842509f168cdde0da056","tid":342547,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1586817&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1586817%26target%3D2&d=eFCPNVMjHz0DGIyw2BCYk%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=66856699\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1586817%26target%3D2&h=80a5f436\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1586817&amp;target=2</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-04-23<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/04/23/116733/i_510x340_930603123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F116733%2Fi_510x340_930603123.jpg&h=35ccb242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　本報早前獨家報道，港鐵須在今年七、八月獲批高鐵營運管理權，始能讓高鐵香港段如期在明年第三季通車。港鐵主席馬時亨昨接受電台訪問時承認，正與政府當局接觸商討高鐵營運事宜，尚未達落實階段，期望能於今年七月新政府上任時與港府簽署合約。<br />\n<br />\n　　他解釋，營運高鐵牽涉的人手預計過千人，港鐵需時招聘及訓練，他明白政府面對不少掣肘，包括處理一地兩檢等，仍期望能盡早處理營運權問題。他又傾向由<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港鐵向政府收取定額營運費</strong></span>，「只收回成本，另加少許費用」，認為較分帳模式簡單，能較快與政府達成共識，但尚未計算實際數目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170423/s00001/1492884259689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170423%2Fs00001%2F1492884259689&d=eFCPNVMjHz0DGIyw2BCYk%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=3559875d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170423%2Fs00001%2F1492884259689&h=0ca61638\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170423/s00001/1492884259689</a><br />\n<br />\n田北辰：定額減改善服務誘因<br />\n<br />\n如港鐵向港府收取定額營運費，將不受高鐵賺蝕影響，立法會鐵路事宜小組主席田北辰認為對高鐵運作未必有利，擔心港鐵無誘因做好服務，變相令政府承擔所有風險。"},{"pid":"b5f6611c653ce3cea65e641c40d8fb413091af62","tid":342547,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"交稅既人比"},{"pid":"8b57b8bd288093a86281b01d2f985cf6229743d0","tid":342547,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fffb903f5f390410970caaee966bc5715a20a93","tid":342547,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T16:52:31.000Z","msg":"呢個奸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668e5a76b5aaa3380d0b1fe2067d14edba38e529","tid":342547,"uid":110286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:10:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39eceb44df4155dc97b019143a182f9edb1fc6e6","tid":342547,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:19:58.000Z","msg":"政府包底<br />\n咪即係市民包底囉"},{"pid":"cca6555256ef089c401260b29137f6a4bfae1f21","tid":342547,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府包底<br />\n咪即係市民包底囉</blockquote><br />\n可以加價,全包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6b0ba8671af1cdcd4d280fe5a544bbbccd4e25","tid":342547,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:21:02.000Z","msg":"食左誠實豆沙包？"},{"pid":"000a33c3bec41c4b32551fcb76c40244f123c514","tid":342547,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T00:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重倉66，無撚敵</blockquote><br 